<div class="space-y-5 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8">
    <div class="rounded-lg">
        <details class="group p-10">
            <summary class="flex items-center cursor-pointer list-none">
                <div
                    class="grid grid-cols-1 items-center lg:gap-10 lg:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-2"
                >
                    <div class="flex flex-col space-y-10">
                        <div
                            class="flex flex-row items-center lg:gap-5"
                        >
                            <h1 class="font-bold text-3xl ">
                                Why recyling RAP is the most eco-friendly action
                                in asphalt pavement production.
                            </h1>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <p class="font-thin text-base">
                                According to 37 recopilated studies, per 10% of
                                RAP incorporation in new hot-mix asphalt
                                decreases environmental impact by roughly 28%
                                compared with conventional virgin aggregate
                                mixes.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
                        <div class="flex flex-col justify-center items-center">
                            <Image
                                src="https://placehold.co/600x400/png"
                                width={600}
                                height={400}
                                alt="Figure 1 - WMA usage between 2008-2014 (Christie 2015)"
                            />
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex justify-center items-center lg:col-span-2">
                        <svg
                            class="transition-transform duration-300 group-open:rotate-180"
                            width="64"
                            height="64"
                            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                            fill="none"
